modules.description: Monitors file system events such as file modifications, creations, and deletions using inotify. It handles inotify descriptors, event masks, and provides functions to read and parse event data. Used for real-time file tracking in applications like log monitors or sync tools.

Provides functions to create and manage inotify file descriptors, add and remove watches on file paths, and read event notifications. Works with file descriptors, watch descriptors, event kinds, and event records containing path information and cookies. Used to monitor file system changes, such as tracking file movements or detecting modifications in real-time.
